  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "## What:\r\nI would like to terminate SSL at tiller and use token auth. This is not currently possible.\r\n\r\n## Cause\r\nTiller assumes client cert if ca cert is provided. https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/blob/master/cmd/tiller/tiller.go#L224\r\n\r\n```go\r\nfunc tlsOptions() tlsutil.Options {\r\n    opts := tlsutil.Options{CertFile: certFile, KeyFile: keyFile}\r\n    if tlsVerify {\r\n        opts.CaCertFile = caCertFile\r\n        opts.ClientAuth = tls.RequireAndVerifyClientCert\r\n    }\r\n    return opts\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Fix\r\nThis can be fixed by changing to `opts.ClientAuth = tls.VerifyClientCertIfGiven`\r\n\r\ncc: @fibonacci1729",
